    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p> Internet connection was bad, onward journey was still unclear, where would I be if Steffi ends up, with the blog I was after a few days after my own company would have wanted to have time from me and also work from 3:00 p.m. to 24:00. In addition, a stupid cold that I had brought from Germany did not want to go away. Somehow everything was too much with that at that moment. </p>
        <p> After a long phone call with Steffi and a good hat, I decided the following plan: I stay up to Steffi&rsquo;s arrival in the chic apartment in Dumaguete, put my company on ice and spend more time outside and on the beach. Since now the effort regarding the onset, accommodation search and the pressure <a href="https://www.smest.it" target="_blank"> Smest.it </a> I had enough time for this blog. My travel blog is really important to me. Especially since I know that my aunt read every article in my grandma and both are somehow part of our trips. </p>
        <p> This decision was absolutely right, everything else was just too much on the piece of paper. A few days later I was finally able to go diving again and enjoy my time here. When I finally had Steffi with me and we also traveled from one dream resort to the next, it became much more relaxed. Thanks, Steffi then took me off the writing of the blog articles and so I just had to take care of the online and my work for card making. So everything got much more relaxed. </p>
    </div>
